 <a href="/content/android-candy-mightytext-mighty-awesome" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"><img src="http://www.linuxjournal.com/files/linuxjournal.com/ufiles/imagecache/teaser/nodeimage/story/11513textf1_1.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-teaser" width="100" height="100" /></a> 
  
  


      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/content/android-candy-mightytext-mighty-awesome" title="Android Candy: MightyText, Mighty Awesome">Android Candy: MightyText, Mighty Awesome</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
		By <a href="/users/shawn-powers" title="View user profile.">Shawn Powers</a>&nbsp;<!--|
		Jul 10, 2013 -->
     
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_192 first"><a href="/tag/android" rel="tag" title="">Android</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_799"><a href="/tag/editors-choice" rel="tag" title="">Editors&#039; Choice</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_328"><a href="/tag/mobile" rel="tag" title="">Mobile</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_20 active"><a href="/tag/reviews" rel="tag" title="" class="active">Reviews</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_196 last"><a href="/tag/tech-tips" rel="tag" title="">Tech Tips</a></li>
</ul></div>
      
  	 </div>
    </div>
  
  
    


  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/android-candy-mightytext-mighty-awesome" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

<p>
I'll admit, I've always been impressed with Apple's iMessage
program. With its integration into texting, it seamlessly combines
instant messaging and SMS into a single communication stream. Whether on
an iPhone, iPod, iPad or Macintosh, the messages can be seen and sent
to other Apple devices.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/android-candy-mightytext-mighty-awesome"> more>></a></span></p>
  </div>



  <ul class="links inline"><li class="comment_comments first last"><a href="/content/android-candy-mightytext-mighty-awesome#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting.">24 comments</a></li>
