 <a href="/content/getting-most-nexus-7" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"><img src="http://www.linuxjournal.com/files/linuxjournal.com/ufiles/imagecache/teaser/nodeimage/story/11377c2-2.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-teaser" width="100" height="100" /></a> 
  
  


      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/content/getting-most-nexus-7" title="Getting the Most from the Nexus 7">Getting the Most from the Nexus 7</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
		By <a href="/users/phillip-raymond" title="View user profile.">Phillip Raymond</a>&nbsp;<!--|
		Feb 25, 2013 -->
     
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_192 first"><a href="/tag/android" rel="tag" title="">Android</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_235"><a href="/tag/google" rel="tag" title="">Google</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_328"><a href="/tag/mobile" rel="tag" title="">Mobile</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_826"><a href="/tag/nexus" rel="tag" title="">Nexus</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_20 last active"><a href="/tag/reviews" rel="tag" title="" class="active">Reviews</a></li>
</ul></div>
      
  	 </div>
    </div>
  
  
    


  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/getting-most-nexus-7" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

<p>
The ASUS/Google Nexus 7 arrived at my door on August 1, 2012 with a lot
of anticipation from both me and the rest of the consumer electronics
world. A quad-core Tegra 3 processor from NVIDIA, a 1200x800
HD IPS display covered with the latest scratch-resistant Corning Gorilla
Glass and a 1.2 megapixel front-facing camera were among its most notable cool
features.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/getting-most-nexus-7"> more>></a></span></p>
  </div>



  <ul class="links inline"><li class="comment_comments first last"><a href="/content/getting-most-nexus-7#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting.">11 comments</a></li>
</ul>
