</ul></div>
      
  	 </div>
    </div>
  
  
    


  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/switching-chromium" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        


<p>
For someone who works with, writes about and teaches cutting-edge
technologies, I tend to be a bit of a laggard when adopting new ones.
I upgrade my laptop and servers very conservatively.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/switching-chromium"> more>></a></span></p>
